parameters:
Crew Member: In the Demon Continent,
once every four years, a martial arts
tournament is held where one's strength
is put to the test.

Crew Member: The candidates for the
championship are the members of the
Blue Knight Order, which is renowned
in the Demon Continent.

Crew Member: Especially the captain,
despite being the youngest, is rumored
to be the greatest swordsman in history.

Maid: I'm sorry, it's not yet time for a
meal...

Maid: I'm currently preparing your
meal...! Please wait a little longer!

Captain: It will take about two weeks to
reach the Demon Continent.

Captain: There's also a bath on the
upper floor, so please enjoy your
journey on the ship leisurely.

Zerachiel: (This person gives off a
similar vibe to Lord Eden...)

???: Why are you trying to help the
Saintess?

????: Regardless of the reason, the fact
that you humiliated me remains
unchanged.

????: However, you are trying to help
the Saintess.

???: If you leave it alone, revenge
will be complete, won't it?
????: Why are you trying to help?

Zerachiel: Honestly, I hate Effy. I
really hate her.

Zerachiel: But, she looked so miserable
right in front of me.

Zerachiel: Even now, she's suffering. If
I leave her alone, she might even die.

Zerachiel: There's no way I can just
leave someone in distress right in front
of me.

Zerachiel: And once she wakes up, I want
to give her a thorough revenge.

Zerachiel: I won't allow you to die
before me.

???: Let me protect the saintess. Oh
maiden with white wings.

Zerachiel: Of course, I promise. I will
help Effy.
????: Ah, I'm looking forward to it.

???: When you keep your promise, I will
bestow my power upon you.

Zerachiel: (Who was that person just
now...)

Zerachiel: (It seems like they knew
about me...)

I will show you that I can protect the
saintess. Oh girl with white wings.

Zerachiel: (That person... seems to have
known that I'm an angel)
